and do not know his whereabout, and if there is a difficult work which he is unable to do, should recite YAA AWWALO 1000 times in the Friday Eve (shab’e Juma) will find the lost one and every difficult will be eased.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh agar koi shakhs ghaaeb ho gaya ho aur us ki koi khabar na mil rahi ho, ya koi bohot hi mushkil kaam ho, jo ho hi na raha ho to 40 shab’e Juma har shab 1000 martaba YAA AWWALO ka vird kiya jaaye to ghaaeb haazir hoga aur har mushkil aasaan ho jaayegi.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ اگر کوئی شخص غائب ہوگیا ہو اور اس کی کوئی خبر نہ مل رہی ہو، یا کوئی بہت ہی مشکل کام ہو جو ہو کے نہ دے رہا ہو تو 40 شب جمعہ ہر شب 1000 بار ’’یَا اَوَّلُ‘‘ کا ورد کیا جائے تو غائب حاضر ہوگا اور ہر مشکل آسان ہوجائے گی۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "Arab